id: 2644
name: The Gauntlet
power: 2
text: |
  A player CAN, by announcement, Notice the Gauntlet, specifying a
  single player that owns 5 or more stones. When e does, the
  specified player Wields the Gauntlet.

  When a player Wields the Gauntlet, e wins the game, then all
  existing stones are transferred to Agora.
